            <a href="#advisor-view" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50">
              üßë‚Äçüè´ Advisor View
            </a>
            <a href="#admin-view" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50">
