          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Student View (regular two-column layout) -->
  <section id="student-view" class="rounded-3xl bg-white px-8 py-10 md:py-14 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 mb-20 md:mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 border-l-4 border-[#500000] pl-4">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5f0eb] text-xl">üéì</div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Role</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#500000]">Student View</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-xl text-sm text-slate-600">Manage assigned surveys, track completion, and review advisor feedback in one place.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Pending Surveys</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>View surveys assigned to you that are not yet completed.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Completed Surveys</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Completed surveys appear here and can be reviewed anytime.</li>
              <li>Advisor feedback, when provided, appears below the survey.</li>
              <li>Surveys are downloadable as PDFs for records.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Notifications</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Shows recent reminders and updates related to your surveys and feedback.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- (Advisor section consolidated below) -->

    <!-- Advisor View (regular two-column layout) -->
  <section id="advisor-view" class="rounded-3xl bg-white px-8 py-10 md:py-14 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 mb-20 md:mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 border-l-4 border-[#500000] pl-4">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#f5f0eb] text-xl">üßë‚Äçüè´</div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Role</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#500000]">Advisor View</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-xl text-sm text-slate-600">Monitor advisee progress, assign surveys, and provide structured feedback to students.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Student Records</span></p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>View students and their tracks in a single list.</li>
            <li>Use <span class="font-semibold">Review</span> to provide feedback on completed surveys.</li>
            <li>After submitting feedback the action is changeable via <span class="font-semibold">Edit Feedback</span>.</li>
            <li>Download surveys and feedback for documentation.</li>
            <li>Students see submitted feedback in their Completed Surveys section.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Surveys</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Assign surveys to individual students when needed.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Notifications</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>View updates related to assigned surveys or feedback deadlines.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-medium text-slate-900"><span class="text-[#500000] font-semibold">Manage Students</span></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
